title: FortiGate CVE Summary
agents: fortigate
catalog: network/fortinet
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check optionally queries OpenCVE for the configured Fortinet product via the FortiGate special agent and reports the total
 number of CVEs. Thresholds for WARN/CRIT are supplied by the special agent rule.
item:
 This check has no item. One service is discovered per FortiGate host when the OpenCVE integration is enabled.
group: Security
parameters:
 Thresholds for WARN and CRIT are taken from the special agent parameters and therefore no separate ruleset is required.
perfdata:
 cves_total: Total number of CVEs reported by OpenCVE for the vendor/product combination.
